{
  "stem": "10710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the food was-- was also very bad in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Some people who had good positions helped themselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we were new ones there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We just came in, so-- so they took advantage of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We slept in the morning-- during the-- it was at night there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody else slept during the day there, so there was not-- nothing yours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't leave anything because there were night shifts and day shifts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the night shifts slept during the day, and the people who worked during the day slept there at night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a lager-- there was a barrack Alteste, like a kapo who was taking care of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was like-- like a guard, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He did whatever he wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you did something wrong, he punished you, and-- and do all kind of bad things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a very, a very-- the camp was horrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You were afraid to go somewhere because you didn't know what-- whom you could meet there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And especially when you met Goeth or somebody, with his dogs or with things, you-- you were-- you were afraid you'd be torn apart.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We worked there in that camp very hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember one thing the kapo did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a Jewish kapo from the Steinbruch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when lunchtime came, he gave us-- we got little tickets to get a lunch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Each one got a little bit soup, a little watery soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You stayed in line for this and then you ate it up because you couldn't leave anything or somebody else would take it away from him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he gave me an extra ticket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I should have two lunches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know, he felt sorry for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He had a few tickets.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
